<report type:"WARNING">
  description : "6.4.1 Ensure mail forwarding rules are reviewed at least weekly"
  info        : "The Exchange Online environment can be configured in a way that allows for automatic forwarding of e-mail. This can be done using Transport Rules in the Admin Center, Auto Forwarding per mailbox, and client-based rules in Outlook. Administrators and users both are given several methods to automatically and quickly send e-mails outside of your organization.

Rationale:

